<h3>CEPT Organisation Control Page</h3>
<p>This page is for use by the Organisation Manager to enable monitoring and control of the
CEPT process. It shows the progress front line staff, have made in completing the CEPT
process. The Organisation Manager can view the detail for each function or policy and
contact the front line staff as required.</p>
<p>Table 1 lists all the functions and policies identified by the local authority and whether
the CEPT process has been started, completed or approved by section.</p>
<p>Table 2 shows the distribution of overall priority scores (1 to 5) and impact dscores (H,
M, L) for policies and functions that have been completed for all three sections and have
been approved.</p>
